                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><xi:include href="../encodingdesc.xml" parse="xml"/></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_gakʼon" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>gakʼon</orth></form><sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>поворот</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>turn</q></abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>извилина</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>curve</q></abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>зигзаг</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>zigzag</q></abv:tr></sense></sense><re><form type="lemma"><orth>gakʼon-makʼon</orth></form><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>извилистый</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>twisting</q></abv:tr></sense></re><abv:exampleGrp><abv:example><quote>Mlety gakʼættæ</quote><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>Млетские зигзаги (на Военно-грузинской дороге)</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>Mleti zigzags (on the Georgian Military Road)</q></abv:tr></abv:example></abv:exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Конечное %i-on%i, вероятно, суффикс; %igakʼ-%i вместе с <ref type="xr" target="#entry_gakk"/> (см. выше) можно сблизить с <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>k’ak’va</w> <gloss><q>изгибать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w>kʼakʼvi</w> <gloss><q>крюк</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">The final %i-on%i is probably a suffix; %igakʼ-%i together with <ref type="xr" target="#entry_gakk"/> (see above) may be connected with <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><lang/> <w>k’ak’va</w> <gloss><q>bend</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ka"><w>kʼakʼvi</w> <gloss><q>hook</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>